songs.title: La Leaker Freestyle
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Shoutout uzi man
Hahaha
I can't lose
𝙞 𝙖𝙞𝙣𝙩 𝙨𝙘𝙖𝙧𝙚𝙙 𝙤𝙛 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙢𝙤𝙩𝙝𝙚𝙧𝙛𝙪𝙘𝙠𝙚𝙧𝙨
*Mumbles* I can't lose
I can't lose

[Verse]
Uh
Every track i just killed shit cos i gotta murder my competitors
Broke nigga trying to talk cash brought the racks out just to shut him up
New bitch bad had to switch up
Now my old hoe says i'm dead to her
Everyday gotta thank god baby can't you see that nigga blessing us
Flying through the with doors up
This an i8 not a Tesla
Used to wait for the link car now its Benihanas' on the regular
Mama worried when I'm in the street but i keep it on me what you stressing for?
Glizzy toting i can't tussle with you i got 30 shots for a wrestler
Play crazy catch a head shot
We was taught to shoot from the neck and up
My shorties reckless when they in the hood
Ol' heads know it ain't no checking us
We be turnt for givenchy
Bitch its gucci gang to the death of us
Hotnem on it they just keep sliding
Imma keep supplying ain't no letting up
Niggas high still gone make it happen
We can't catch em loafing we gotta set em up
Got the drop, waiting by his crib
When he walk out we gone wet him up
.40 go BOW to yo A
Shots knock him out of bounds if he play
We put him in the ground with the K
That choppa clear a crowd when it spray
My uncle went on trial for the ye
I used to dream of pounds in the safe
I'm flying through the clouds skipping states
Count up a 100 thou with my bae
They try take my down with the hey
It be the nigga smiling in your face
I'm with it getting wild everyday
That's why i move around with the apes
Like Ay
Please don't start with us we won't play cool
All em shooters charged up you know what they do
Money keep coming in I can't lose
Had to switch it up with the drip, Dolce shoes
I be balling on em like I'm Ivo
I was posted with my soldiers
We was trapping hard for survival
I was posted on the corner where we dropped a g for disciples
All of my niggas demons we don't abide by the Bible

[Outro]

This is how we doing it POLO G
Chicago
I fuck with polo too he pulled up like pull the beat up
Lets get straight to it
I ain't even staying on i wanna shoutout dj los man for connecting the dots too man
He was like yo i gotta come up there and spit some bars man
Thank you brother
Shoutout dj los shoutout la leakers man
Thank you brother
You know what it is power 106
Number 1 for hip hop lift off show
